data.description: Hot Property! Gorgeous 2 bed 3 bath townhome with attached 2 car garage! End unit with views from balcony and full size driveway! This property has white Cabinets and quartz countertops, all stainless steel kitchen appliances gives this home a modern clean feel and look. Flooring is vinyl plank throughout with carpet on stairs. 2" faux wood blinds, flooring, USB outlets at kitchen & master, and much more! Community pool and park! Priced to sell!
